{
  "stem": "5255.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we still didn't get any food, and we had to stay another day.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And another 50% of them died.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Finally, from the 2,000 people that marched out of our camp, maybe 700 survived to enter Buchenwald.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And we got to Buchenwald, and we got in a, like, isolation camp.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Because they had a regular camp, and they have newcomers, and they didn't want to mix both groups up.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So we were what we called the small camp in Buchenwald.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And after being there for a couple of weeks, they sent us away.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] They send us out to a camp by the name of Ohrdruf.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Ohrdruf, it was a bad camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And there were Russians in that camp, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and there were Ukraine.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Ukraine.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And these guards that guard us were Germans and Ukraines, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and the prisoners were also Ukraines.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So there were members of the Russian army that did not behave in their regular camps were sent to this particular camp called-- they used to call it [NON-ENGLISH] camp.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] camp was a punishable camp, to punish the prisoners that did not behave.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there were really not that much to do there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Did you have trouble from those tough prisoners?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "These-- these-- these Ukrainians, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] they mistreated these-- they were prisoners-- they mistreated the Jews.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were tall, gigantic people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when we stayed in line to get our bread ration, they used to grab it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If we didn't take the ration, the bread ration, and put it into our shirts fast enough, they grabbed it out of the hands.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So there were a lot of prisoners, didn't eat for days.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They died of starvation.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
